title: Fix #4 -- Add event information page (#19)
message:
Fix #4 -- Add event information page (#19)

* added Activity and View for Eventinfo View

* small typo

* added status call to PretixApi

* added a first textview as proof of concept

* added a model to represent the cards within the adapter system for androids listviews
created an adapter for the event cards

* added method comments

* added card elements for first testing

* added data fields to card objects

* switching adapters

* fixed inflater context bug which results in not applied styles if ApplicationContext is used for inflating

* added gui enhancements to the event card

* added gui enhancements to the item card

* added variations to an eventitemcard

* adjusted manifest to show back arrow

* refactoring from android studio designer

* added translations

* added translations

* added relative layout around an event card
adjusted card margins

* small typo

* reformatted code with android studio

* added clear of adapter data before initial filling

* moved inner classes EventinfoListItem, EventCardItem and EventItemCardItem into own files

* moved variationList out of the loop

* changed text styles to maintain minSdkLevel

* added loading progress bar

* added proper exception handling on communication problems

* added error handling for malformed responses

* added fix for android sdk licensing

* Added SwipeRefreshLayout

* introduced the "setData" method to pull the json parsing out of the ListItem-constructors

* added getData method to recieve the raw JSON data

* update the already inflated convertView to new data and then display it again

* just ignore recycling and display the new card

* use the newly created object to fill the already existing view
